snippet.title: Tower Of Spirit - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1989140/Tower_of_Spirit/

Tower of Spirit is a fast turn-based RPG where your choices matter. Gather a group of unique characters, survive a serie of random encounters and battle your way to reach the enigmatic tower!
